  "texts": [
    "To minimize noise, we used an e-value cutoff of 1 × 10 -10 for COGs and the default model noise cutoff scores for Pfams.",
    "We inferred de novo gene families by running MMseqs2 (ref.",
    "76) v10.6d92c on all amino acid sequences in our reference plasmids and chromosomes.",
    "First, we ran 'mmseqs clusthash' to collapse identical sequences into a non-redundant set for faster execution of the next step; the collapsing was inverted at the end to annotate all genes.",
    "Next, we ran 'mmseqs cluster' to calculate pairwise alignments and then cluster genes that are aligned above a minimum sequence identity threshold (parameter '--min-seq-id')."
  ],
